data.description: Welcome to your tranquil sanctuary. Unwind on the covered patio, gazing upon your yard, expansive greenery, and serene lakes. This meticulously-maintained home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a library/office with French doors, 12’ ceilings, and ample natural light from large windows. The open floor plan is perfect for hosting gatherings, featuring a spacious kitchen island with seating adjacent to a breakfast area. Situated in a dynamic community with amenities such as pools, playgrounds, and a recreation center, it offers convenient access to Pearland TC, the medical center, and downtown. ALL brick exterior with no rear neighbors. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough
